main event: A civilian reported sighting a UFO in Chicago, Illinois on September 1, 1965.
interesting points: The object was observed for 10 to 25 minutes and moved in a northerly direction,The observer did not feel the object was artificial and noted no unusual sounds or landing,Initially described as a round or ellipsoid green object moving swiftly in a circular motion,The object appeared luminous and was seen multiple times by civilians and military personnel,Observations recorded on subsequent dates included additional sightings with varying descriptions and details.
